data.description: Welcome home to this 6 bedroom, 3 bath home in the Turnberry Subdivision! This home has approximately 4500 sq ft of finished space and boasts a three-car tandem garage, deck, patio area perfect for entertaining guests. The family room has cathedral ceilings and a fireplace that is perfect for cozy evenings, while the large updated eat-in kitchen with a breakfast island, stainless steel appliances, and large walk-in pantry is ideal for those who love to cook and entertain guests. Large open layout, a formal dining room, and a first-floor laundry room with a wash sink add to the home's overall appeal. The master suite is complete with dual walk-in closets, a whirlpool tub, separate shower, and double vanity. The partially finished basement includes a recreational room, an office space, and an additional bedroom. Call today for your private showing!
